OpenDoc addresses this need for task-centric computing by making it easy to=
 integrate different content types and functionality rather than copy-and-p=
aste data from one application to another, a user can drag-and-drop their f=
avorite features, such as tools to hand text, graphics, or Internet connect=
ions into one seamless workspace.

Copilot Pages is obviously dramatically different than OpenDoc=E2=80=99s un=
wieldy attempt of embedding different applications within one document, but=
 it=E2=80=99s striking how similar the vision is, including the provisions =
for 3rd-party software; back to Nadella:

( https://videopress.com/embed/cXxs7I7H?hd=3D1&cover=3D1&loop=3D0&autoPlay=
